      "id": "PopularPost33713",
      "post_content": "True, on the other hand thats a 5/3 sojourner, in naya that means it can also gain first strike, vigilance, indestructibility, regeneration, and etc. Then even if it dies you make one of your creatures somewhat stronger. If you play with crystallization, you can use the 1/1 counter to exile the creature its pacifying. On jund, the counter can also give benefits to creatures, like improving the amount of saprolings a mycoloth can create on upkeep. For ravnica, the counter can be used to activate simic cards.",
      "posted_by": "Donovan_Fabian",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost33713\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_post\">True, on the other hand thats a 5/3 sojourner, in naya that means it can also gain first strike, vigilance, indestructibility, regeneration, and etc.  Then even if it dies you make one of your creatures somewhat stronger.  If you play with crystallization, you can use the 1/1 counter to exile the creature its pacifying.  On jund, the counter can also give benefits to creatures, like improving the amount of saprolings a mycoloth can create on upkeep.  For ravnica, the counter can be used to activate simic cards.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2942\">Donovan_Fabian</span>\r\n                                (11/5/2009 3:41:31 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl00_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSol