      "id": "PopularPost344644",
      "post_content": "Naya Sojourners ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol)![Green](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=G&type=symbol)  \n**Instant  \nNaya Sojourners can't be countered by spells or abilities.**  \nPut a +1/+1 counter on target creature.  \nDraw a card.  \n  \nWe have [Aggressive Urge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aggressive Urge), [Instill Infection](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Instill Infection), and various strictly-better [Battlegrowth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Battlegrowth)s, but still no cantrip instant +1/+1 counter.",
      "posted_by": "HuntingDrake",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost344644\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Naya Sojourners <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Green\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=G&amp;type=symbol\"/><br/><b>Instant<br/>Naya Sojourners can't be countered by spells or abilities.</b><br/>Put a +1/+1 counter on target creature.<br/>Draw a card.<br/><br/>We have <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aggressive Urge\">Aggressive Urge</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Instill Infection\">Instill Infection</a>, and various strictly-better <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Battlegrowth\">Battlegrowth</a>s, but still no cantrip instant +1/+1 counter.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy26712\">HuntingDrake</span>\r\n                                (10/4/2013 2:27:12 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubC