      "id": "PopularPost21281",
      "post_content": "Dang, would have been rewriting the [Sojourners](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sojourners) cycle to \"*When ~ is put into a graveyard, you may have it deal 1 damage to target creature or player*.\" been so difficult?  \nThis wouldn't have been gamebreaking either with that shortened text. Of course there is still a notable difference since it triggered from any discard effect this way.  \nBut it could have been an interesting addition to madness decks then. ",
