      "post_content": "On constructed: None of the cards in this cycle as very good, and this, while one of the better ones, clearly never broke out into standard. No surprise there.\n  \nOn limited: It all depends on what colors you're going. The great part about this cycle is that they work even if you're without their other colors. Nothing game-breaking, though.\n  \nMiscellaneous: They randomly made this promo, y'know.",
